Yize kunjalo abakwa-Eskom izolo bathumele isitatimende baxwayise ukuthi awusetshenziswe kahle ugesi njengoba kungenzeka uphinde ucinywe uma bebhekana nengcindezi. “I-Eskom izoqhubeka isebenzise ugesi obekelwe izimo eziphuthumayo uma kunesidingo ngalesi sikhathi. “Yize kunjalo, sifisa ukukhumbuza amakhasimende ethu ukuthi isimo asikabi sihle futhi ngeke sikwazi ukuqagela ukuthi singashintsha nini,” kusho abakwa-Eskom esitatimendeni esithunyelwe abezindaba. NgeSonto ugesi awuzange ucinywe, bathe ngo-6.30 ekuseni amandla kagesi abengu- 14,574MW. Ithimba lakwa-Eskom kuthiwa liyaqhubeka nokuqapha isimo ngesikhathi samaholidi, ukuze banciphise amathuba wokuba ugesi ucinywe. “Siyawanxusa amakhasimende ethu ukuba ehlise ukusetshenziswa kukagesi, ukuze ugesi ungacinywa,” kusho abakwa-Eskom. 